data.description: Here's your chance to own a "like new home" (built in 2022) that's only 8 minutes from downtown Richmond and close to shopping!!! This home features a nice, modern floor plan with lots of light, openness, and upgrades. Some of the upgrades include LVP flooring throughout first floor, rear deck, recessed lighting, modern fixtures, and stainless steel appliances. The home qualifies for a $10,000 grant to cover your down payment, by way of the Pathway Home Program. This program is offered by George Mason Mortgage and there's no mortgage insurance, resulting in lower mortgage payment.
